reviewText: I like all the Travis movies, because they bleep out the bad words.  I have young kids that love this stuff, as far as moto-cross movies goes and other thrill adventure movies goes, this is pretty clean entertainment.
omg the stunts these guys to are crazy..some are in the season 1 show but they are great and leaves you saying omg or crazy durning the stunts. i totally would recommend this dvd.
